   "updated": 1,
   "link": null,
   "locked": false,
   "text": "• AWS landing zone (Org, SCP, SSO), EKS 1.34 + Karpenter,\n  TGW hub-spoke, Cilium, GPU-кластер (H100)\n• GitOps: ArgoCD + Kargo; политика: OPA/Gatekeeper,\n  Kyverno, Checkov; External Secrets, Cosign\n• 22 Terraform-модуля + Terragrunt live\n• Продукт: transaction-analytics (3-tier)",
   "fontSize": 14,
   "fontFamily": 1,
   "textAlign": "left",
   "verticalAlign": "top",
   "baseline": 14,
   "containerId": null,
   "originalText": "• AWS landing zone (Org, SCP, SSO), EKS 1.34 + Karpenter,\n  TGW hub-spoke, Cilium, GPU-кластер (H100)\n• GitOps: ArgoCD + Kargo; политика: OPA/Gatekeeper,\n  Kyverno, Checkov; External Secrets, Cosign\n• 22 Terraform-модуля + Terragrunt live\n• Продукт: transaction-analytics (3-tier)",
   "lineHeight": 1.25
